Municipio Ocozocautla. Steep walled limestone canyon of Rio de Venta near Cascada El Aquacero. 15 km W of Ocozocuautla on Hwy. 190, then 3 km N. Elev. 2000-2500 ft. Tropical dry forest. 16.46'N, 93.33'W.
